    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Walls with a masonry face or revetment that is attached, but not bonded, to the body of the wall and does not exert a common reaction under load. Walls with a masonry face or revetment that is attached, but not bonded, to the body of the wall and does not exert a common reaction under load.</Note_Text>
